:name:
Counsel

:coretxt:
The character is able to heal the mind.
Some people are exeptional at this.
Character can give healing to mentally(non-vigor) wounded character.
Character gives advice to the wounded. 
For example, with \AbilityNameMusic{}, \AbilityNameReligion{}, \AbilityNameExpression{}, or \AbilityNameSpeak{}.
If person follows this advice, he is healed by amount of success.

:cost:
1 related pool, spend by user


:tags:
Ability
Music
Religion
Expression
Speak
